_:N7c1b1efb2670420881a8798c36e37db5 <http://schema.org/description> "The UK Commission on Covid Commemoration has been established to secure a broad consensus from across the whole of the United Kingdom on how we commemorate the COVID-19 pandemic and mark this distinctive period in our history at a national and community level. The Commission is expected to report to the Prime Minister by the end of March 2023. UK Commission on Covid Commemoration works with the Cabinet Office ." <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/jsonld> .
